dc_title_s: Police Districts City of Milwaukee, WI 2009
dc_description_s: This data represents police districts for the City of Milwaukee, Wisconsin in 2009. [Milwaukee Police Department (MPD) district polygons. Contains the current MPD Police Districts. These boundaries went into effect on July 12, 2009.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data, please visit: https://data.milwaukee.gov/dataset/milwaukee-police-district
